Imo,
<br />
Any hps will help.  Dont forget, you would pay BIG PLAT for items with +100hps on them.  And 2% extra hit points is exactly the same as 2% damage avoidance in terms of how much longer you'll live over time.  But damage avoidance has the chance to waste more healing mana - you are getting a CH anyways what good is it to dodge that attack unless it is gonna kill you?  You have a better chance of surviving that blow if you ALWAYS have an extra few hundred health, rather than having that 2%, or 5%, or 10% chance of dodging it.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
