			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Beastlord isnt a mitigation class, its an avoidance class. NA helps with totally avoiding a hit so that 2k hit just turned into a 0point wiff. I noticed now that I accidently typed mitigate instead of avoid in my post, sorry about that, I meant avoid and not mitigate in every spot I typed mitigate, hehe..
<br />

<br />
And yes, if your eating AEs more hps help, but even in that case we are in a bit different position from rouges as we have Chloroblast at L62 which is a very good heal to use incase the big heals are being delayed a bit. For a rogue you either have to burn some healing potion you have spent a lot of cash on or just hope that the healers pay enough attention that you get a heal before you get too low, so IMO a rogue would be more inclined to go for hps to ensure you give the healers more time to make sure you get healed.. 
<br />

<br />
A beastlord while not being a good tank can tank and sometimes do tank, even on boss mobs, preslowing can really get you aggro quickly, which means that we will probably be saving our discs for defensive anyways incase we get aggro. Which is also different from a rogue, if a rogue is tanking somethings gone terribly wrong somewhere (and even if you got enough ac and hps for tanking for a bit the mob is facing completly the wrong way so that no rogue can BS for dps), if a beastlord is tanking it is probably just because we preslowed..
<br />

<br />

<br />
Thats why I feel its more important with CA for us than ND.
<br />

<br />
And if its AEs your worried about then you *will* have a healer for your group, if your worried about if the mob aggros you then the few extra hps ND gives as a beastlord wouldnt be more than a single hit, most likely not even half a hit, while CA would most likely at least stop 1 hit that you otherwise wouldnt be able to avoid. Thats my 2cp anyways.<br />_________________<br /><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=360803" target="_blank" OnClick="javascript:window.open('http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=360803','','width=800,height=600'); return false"><img src="http://home.swipnet.se/Nulli-Secundis/pics/DahkarET.jpg" border="0" alt="Click here to inspect"></a></center></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
